NII Holdings Inc.


            
            NII Holdings, Inc. engages in the development and provision of wireless communication services. It offers mobile telephone voice, wireless data, push-to-talk services, business solutions, and voice and data roaming solutions. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Reston, VA.

            
