Products and Services | Nii Holdings | Multinational Telecommunications Company































 You have Javascript disabled. This site is best experienced with Javascript. We recommend you enable Javascript, and reload the page.
 You have Javascript disabled. This site is requires Javascript when browsing on mobile. We recommend you enable Javascript, and reload the page.
 You have Javascript disabled. When browsing this site with Internet Explorer 8 or older Javascript is required. You must enable Javascript and reload the page, or upgrade to a modern web browser.

