Headquartered in Reston, VA, NII Holdings, Inc., formerly known as Nextel International, is a provider of institutional wireless communication services in several Latin American markets including Argentina, Brazil, Mexico, Peru, and Chile.
IT Priorities:
•Improving network security 
•Maintaining IT infrastructure
•Increasing IT presence

IT Structure:
•Company is headquartered in Reston, VA
•NII Holdings' information technology department provides day-to-day technical support to internal employees and participates in providing strategies for future business growth. The Chief Technology Officer handles… MoreIT Priorities:
•Improving network security 
•Maintaining IT infrastructure
•Increasing IT presence

IT Structure:
•Company is headquartered in Reston, VA
•NII Holdings' information technology department provides day-to-day technical support to internal employees and participates in providing strategies for future business growth. The Chief Technology Officer handles the global product-side technology development, and operations across the company.
•The IT department is comprised of several smaller units including the following: IT strategy, emerging technologies, wireless services, financial systems, data architecture, infrastructure sourcing and telecommunications.

IT Vendors:
•The organization maintains a solid Oracle environment, across the company. The company uses cloud-based email, in the form of Gmail and Google Apps.





