nii holdings inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Communications
Industry: Telecom
Sub-Industry: Telecom Carriers
NII Holdings Inc., provides mobile communications for business customers in Latin America. The Company has operations in Argentina, Brazil, Chile, Mexico, and Peru, offering a fully integrated wireless communications tool with digital cellular service, text and numeric paging, wireless internet access, and a digital two-way radio feature.




